Ida Erios Nantaba bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị Uganda
Ọ bụ Minista Steeti na Ministri Ozi na Nkà na Ụzụ Mmekọrịta nke Uganda

A họpụtara ya n'ọkwa ahụ na 6 June 2016. Tupu nke ahụ, site na 15 August 2012 ruo 6 June 2016, ọ bụ Minista nke Steeti maka Ala na Cabinet nke Uganda. Nantaba bụkwa onye a họpụtara ka ọ bụrụ onye omeiwu maka ụmụ nwanyị na mpaghara Kayunga.
A mụrụ ya na Kayunga District na 20 Disemba 1979. Nna ya nwụrụ na 1984 ma hapụ ya na nne ya onye lekọtara ya na nkwado nke nwanne ya nwoke nke okenye (Samuel Kabenge Bamulumbye) onye nketa nna ya
Ọ gara Ndeeba Primary School na Kayunga District site na 1986 ruo 1992, ebe ọ gụsịrị ule Primary Leaving Examinations
Otú ọ dị, nne ya na nwanne ya nwoke nke okenye enweghị ego zuru ezu iji kpọga ya n'ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị dị mma n'ihi ya ọ sonyeere Ndeeba Senior Secondary School maka S1 ya na 1993
Ọ kwagara ka ya na nwanne ya nwoke nke okenye nọrọ n'obodo Kisoga, ka dị na mpaghara Kayunga
Ndị obodo Kisoga na-echeta otú nwanne ya nwoke si ebuga ya n'ịnyịnya ígwè gaa ụlọ akwụkwọ, ihe dị ka kilota 14 (8.7 mi) site n'ụlọ ha, kwa ụbọchị
N'afọ 1994, nne Nantaba nwetara ego, a kwagara Nantaba site na Ndeeba SSS gaa Katikamu SDA SSS ebe ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ site na Senior 2 ruo Senior 4 (Uganda Certificate of Education)
A nabatara ya na Mukono Town Academy maka A' Level ya nke ọ gụsịrị na Nọvemba 1998
Na 26 Septemba 1999, a nabatara Nantaba na Mahadum Makerere, maka nzere bachelọ na njem nleta
O mere ọrụ nyocha nke ụmụ akwụkwọ na-agụsị akwụkwọ, "Medicinal Plants As Tourism Potential: Case Study of Uganda Wildlife Educational Center (UWEC)", nke Prọfesọ J
B
Nyakaana lekọtara
Nantaba nwere nzere Bachelor of Tourism, nke ọ nwetara na 2003 na Mahadum Makerere.
N'afọ puku abụọ na atọ , mgbe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na Makerere, ọ rụrụ ọrụ dị ka onye ọrụ njem nleta na Pearl of Africa Tours and Travel Limited
Ọ hapụrụ ọrụ ahụ na ngwụcha afọ 2003
Malite n'afọ 2005, ọ rụrụ ọrụ na bọọdụ ndị nduzi nke Jordan Laboratories Limited, onye na-ekesa ihe foto na ihe obibi akwụkwọ
N'afọ 2010, ọ sonyeere ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị na-arụsi ọrụ ike site n'ịgba ọsọ na Kayunga District Women's Parliamentary Constituency
O meriri na ntuli aka nke NRM site na imeri onye nọ n'ọkwa, Florence Naiga

N'afọ 2011, a họpụtara ya n'oge ntuli aka. N'ime mgbanwe nke ndị kansụl na 15 Ọgọstụ 2012, a họpụtara ya dị ka Minista Steeti maka Ala, na-anọchi Sarah Opendi Achieng. Mgbe izu ole na ole nke mkparịta ụka nkwenye dị ogologo gasịrị, Kọmitii Ntinye aha nke Nzukọ Ndị Omeiwu mechara kwado nhọpụta ya na 23 Ọktoba 2012.

N'oge ntuli aka ndị omeiwu nke afọ 2016, Nantaba meriri n'oge ntuziaka nke National Resistance Movement (NRM), otu ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị ya n'oge ahụ. Ọ hapụrụ òtù ahụ, na-ekwu na ọ bụ ihe na-akpali akpali n'oge ntuli aka, dịka ọ dọrọ aka ná ntị na mbụ. N'oge ntuli aka mba nke e mere na 18 Febụwarị 2016, Nantaba, onye gbara ọsọ dị ka onye na-azọ onwe ya, nwetara vootu 86,057 megide Ruth Nakacwa, onye nwetara vootu 13,184. N'agbanyeghị na ọ hapụrụ òtù NRM na-achị achị, a họpụtara ya dị ka Minista nke steeti maka ICT na 6 June 2016.

N'abalị iri abụọ na anọ n'ọnwa Machị afọ pụkụ abụọ na iri na itoolu , Nantaba tinyere aka n'ihe mere nke mere ka ndị uwe ojii Uganda kee onye aka ya dị ọcha ma gbagbuo ya. Nantaba chere n'ụzọ na-ezighi ezi na nwoke ahụ, Ronald Ssebulime, na-eso ha na ọgba tum tum ya na Kayunga District. Mgbe a chụchara Ssebulime, onye uwe ojii jidere Ssebuliame, kee ya aka, ma gbaa ya égbè ugboro abụọ n'obi. Ndị ọrụ gọọmentị na mbụ gbalịrị ikpuchi ihe ahụ merenụ, na-ekwu na ha emebiela mgbalị igbu ọchụ. Mana mgbe iwe obodo gasịrị, ndị uwe ojii wepụtara nkwupụta na-ekwu na onye ọrụ ahụ na-ahụ maka ya.N'oge
